name: 15 Memory Card - Mischa
description: Mischa the white swan is a prima donna from the district of Andalusia. Not only because she has a sweet face, but also because she has an intellectual charm and masters 7 languages. She works at the library her family founded called Shangri La which you can visit on foot since it is not far from the harbor. You just need to walk to the top of the hill and you will see the library near the lighthouse tower.
